dia.vn\/youtube-shorts-chien-luoc-ki-thuat-so.html\/#Quy_danh_cho_video_ngan_tren_Youtube\" title=\"Qu\u1ef9 d\u00e0nh cho video ng\u1eafn tr\u00ean Youtube\">Qu\u1ef9 d\u00e0nh cho video ng\u1eafn tr\u00ean Youtube<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/youtube-shorts-chien-luoc-ki-thuat-so.html\/#_Video_ngan_tren_YouTube_la_gi\" title=\"\u00a0Video ng\u1eafn tr\u00ean YouTube l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\">\u00a0Video ng\u1eafn tr\u00ean YouTube l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/youtube-shorts-chien-luoc-ki-thuat-so.html\/#Dac_trung_cua_video_ngan\" title=\"\u0110\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a video ng\u1eafn\">\u0110\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a video ng\u1eafn<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/youtube-shorts-chien-luoc-ki-thuat-so.html\/#Video_ngan_tren_YouTube_co_the_hoat_dong_nhu_the_nao_doi_voi_thuong_hieu_cua_ban\" title=\"Video ng\u1eafn tr\u00ean YouTube c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n?\">Video ng\u1eafn tr\u00ean YouTube c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/youtube-shorts-chien-luoc-ki-thuat-so.html\/#Kha_nang_tiep_can\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/youtube-shorts-chien-luoc-ki-thuat-so.html\/#Cong_cu_tim_kiem_video\" title=\"C\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm video\">C\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm video<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/youtube-shorts-chien-luoc-ki-thuat-so.html\/#Thu_vien_noi_dung\" title=\"Th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i dung\">Th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i dung<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/youtube-shorts-chien-luoc-ki-thuat-so.html\/#Han_che\" title=\"H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>H\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng internet \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy c\u1eadp tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb kh\u00e1c nhau.\u00a0Do \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00eam v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng n\u1ed9i dung d\u1ea1ng ng\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Snapchat Stories,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/TikTok\">TikTok<\/a>\u00a0v\u00e0 Instagram Reels, YouTube \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh:\u00a0<strong>YouTube Shorts<\/strong>\u00a0.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_danh_cho_video_ngan_tren_Youtube\"><\/span>Qu\u1ef9 d\u00e0nh cho video ng\u1eafn tr\u00ean Youtube<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p align=\"justify\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng,\u00a0<strong>YouTube Shorts \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf Anh<\/strong> t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2020 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng ph\u1ea1m vi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi +26 qu\u1ed1c gia. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00f4ng ty \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng\u00a0\u00a0Qu\u1ef9 qu\u1ea7n\u00a0ch\u00fang , qu\u1ef9 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la d\u00e0nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf h\u01a1n 30 qu\u1ed1c gia m\u1edbi.\u00a0Tuy nhi\u00ean, TikTok v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng video ng\u1eafn v\u1edbi qu\u1ef9 d\u00e0nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh (200 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 la) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng v\u1ecdt m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n<p align=\"justify\">Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, Facebook v\u00e0 Instagram \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 1 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u00f4 la v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2022 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung v\u00e0 t\u0103ng thu nh\u1eadp th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang h\u1ecd.<\/p>\n<p align=\"justify\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u1ed9i dung video, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ee7 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u1ea1i vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u00eanh trong\u00a0chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1\u00a0c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd hay kh\u00f4ng .\u00a0Video ng\u1eafn c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb n\u1ed9i dung kh\u00f4ng?<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_14969\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14969\" style=\"width: 1103px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-14969 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screenshot_6.png\" alt=\"Video ng\u1eafn \" width=\"1103\" height=\"434\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screenshot_6.png 1103w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screenshot_6-300x118.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screenshot_6-1024x403.png 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screenshot_6-768x302.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1103px) 100vw, 1103px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-14969\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Youtube shorts<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Video_ngan_tren_YouTube_la_gi\"><\/span>\u00a0Video ng\u1eafn tr\u00ean YouTube l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p align=\"justify\">YouTube Shorts l\u00e0 c\u00e1c video ng\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o trong \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng YouTube. D\u00e0nh cho thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e0i t\u1ed1i \u0111a 60 gi\u00e2y<\/li>\n<li>C\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c video d\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng (g\u1eafn th\u1ebb # #shorts).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p align=\"justify\">Nh\u1eefng video d\u1ea1ng ng\u1eafn n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng n\u1ed9i dung d\u1ea1ng ng\u1eafn ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn.<\/p>\n<p align=\"justify\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, YouTube Shorts \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 b\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n \u201cShort shelf\u201d c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang h\u1ecd trong \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng, n\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cu\u1ed9n ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea5p d\u1eef li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn theo thu\u1eadt to\u00e1n, trong \u0111\u00f3 qu\u1ea7n short c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng ng\u1ed3i trong th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n k\u00eanh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung video d\u1ea1ng d\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u00ec qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c bi\u1ec3u m\u1eabu beta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m, n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp s\u1ebd v\u1eabn t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n.<\/p>\n<h2 align=\"justify\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dac_trung_cua_video_ngan\"><\/span>\u0110\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a video ng\u1eafn<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_14971\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14971\" style=\"width: 491px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-14971 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Y.png\" alt=\"Video ng\u1eafn\" width=\"491\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Y.png 491w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Y-268x300.png 268w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 491px) 100vw, 491px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-14971\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a video ng\u1eafn<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p align=\"justify\">M\u1ed9t t\u00ednh n\u0103ng thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a YouTube Shorts bao g\u1ed3m m\u1ed9t camera nhi\u1ec1u \u0111o\u1ea1n cho ph\u00e9p hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 video c\u00f9ng nhau trong c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t khung h\u00ecnh.\u00a0\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a TikTok.\u00a0T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o YouTube Shorts c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 truy c\u1eadp th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n nh\u1ea1c do n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong video c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 TikTok.<\/p>\n<p align=\"justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o l\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i \u00e2m thanh t\u1eeb video c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c (tr\u1eeb khi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd).\u00a0C\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 t\u1ea1o ph\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec1, ch\u00e8n clip t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e1t l\u1ea1i video v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 l\u1ecdc ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda m\u00e0u c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n.\u00a0YouTube, nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi, \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng h\u01a1n khi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Video_ngan_tren_YouTube_co_the_hoat_dong_nhu_the_nao_doi_voi_thuong_hieu_cua_ban\"><\/span>Video ng\u1eafn tr\u00ean YouTube c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u1ed9t nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u1ee7a\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.thinkwithgoogle.com\/feature\/youtube-video-data-watching-habits\/\">Think With Google<\/a>\u00a0cho bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng &#8221;\u00a0<em>50% ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng video tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua h\u00e0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng<\/em> &#8220;. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u00ec n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh mua h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kha_nang_tiep_can\"><\/span>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a YouTube Shorts l\u00e0 n\u00f3 gi\u00fap n\u1ed9i dung video c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng truy c\u1eadp cao. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o n\u1ed9i dung v\u00e0 xem qua thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng video ng\u1eafn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111a d\u1ea1ng h\u00f3a n\u1ed9i dung YouTube \u0111\u1ec3 bao g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n h\u01a1n m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c d\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap thu h\u00fat nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o Gen-Z v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 l\u1edbn.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cong_cu_tim_kiem_video\"><\/span>C\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm video<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn n\u1ed9i dung tr\u00ean YouTube c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u cho\u00e1ng ng\u1ee3p. C\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u01b0a k\u00eanh v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch xem k\u00eanh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm video n\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm n\u1ed9i dung d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c tranh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1ed9i dung theo \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Thu_vien_noi_dung\"><\/span>Th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i dung<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15036\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15036\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15036 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/cardmapr-nl-N8Pnhrcr73o-unsplash-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Thu-vien-hinh-anh\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1710\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/cardmapr-nl-N8Pnhrcr73o-unsplash-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/cardmapr-nl-N8Pnhrcr73o-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/cardmapr-nl-N8Pnhrcr73o-unsplash-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/cardmapr-nl-N8Pnhrcr73o-unsplash-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/cardmapr-nl-N8Pnhrcr73o-unsplash-1536x1026.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/cardmapr-nl-N8Pnhrcr73o-unsplash-2048x1368.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15036\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>V\u00ec video ng\u1eafn tr\u00ean YouTube s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam v\u00e0o th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n k\u00eanh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a video ng\u1eafn:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>YouTube Shorts cho ph\u00e9p nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n xem n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u00e3i m\u00e3i.<\/li>\n<li>T\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c cho nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1edbi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c k\u00eanh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Han_che\"><\/span>H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15038\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15038\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15038 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/nordwood-themes-8LfE0Lywyak-unsplash-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Han-che-cua-Youtube\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/nordwood-themes-8LfE0Lywyak-unsplash-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/nordwood-themes-8LfE0Lywyak-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/nordwood-themes-8LfE0Lywyak-unsplash-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/nordwood-themes-8LfE0Lywyak-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/nordwood-themes-8LfE0Lywyak-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/nordwood-themes-8LfE0Lywyak-unsplash-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15038\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Youtube<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p align=\"justify\">M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p khi t\u1ea3i video ng\u1eafn l\u00ean. Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh thu nh\u1ecf cho video c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. H\u00ecnh thu nh\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a video. C\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00f3 \u00edt quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<\/p>\n<p align=\"justify\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 video kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 video ng\u1eafn:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng camera t\u1ea1o video ng\u1eafn<\/li>\n<li>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ebb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng\u00a0 # ng\u1eafn.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p align=\"justify\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 video t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o k\u1ec7 video ng\u1eafn. V\u00ec c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 quy tr\u00ecnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a YouTube. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed video \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<p align=\"justify\">Ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea3i c\u00e1c video TikTok ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn l\u00ean k\u1ec7 YouTube Shorts. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o video tiktok c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u0103ng video ng\u1eafn l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i. \u0110\u1ea1o v\u0103n v\u00e0 n\u1ed9i dung kh\u00f4ng nguy\u00ean b\u1ea3n l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc, YouTube hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p>B\u00e0i \u0111\u1ecdc th\u00eam:<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/10-cong-cu-manh-me-de-cai-thien-su-hien.html\/\">10 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n tr\u00ean Youtube<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/seo-youtube-moi-thu-ban-can-biet.html\/\">SEO Youtube: M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft\u00a0<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng internet \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy c\u1eadp tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb kh\u00e1c nhau.\u00a0Do \u0111\u00f3